</h2>
<p>
  This year, we created some cultural and creative products to promote iGEM and our project to the public, and these products have been widely loved.
</p>
<h3>Recruitment Postcards and Posters</h3>
<p>
  To introduce iGEM to freshmen, we created postcards and posters. The posters included an introduction to iGEM and some of the achievements of CAU-China. During the welcome event, we showcased these posters to the freshmen in the College of Biological Sciences and distributed our postcards. These materials were well-received by freshmen, sparking significant interest in iGEM and our project. These activities not only promote synthetic biology and iGEM but also allow us to pass down the synthetic biology ideals of CAU-China from generation to generation.
</p>
