<br><br><div class="container"><div class="horizontal-line"></div></div><h1>Summary</h1><div class="container"><div class="horizontal-line"></div></div>
<p>The concept of &#39;teaching according to students&#39; aptitude&#39; is also the educational philosophy of Confucius, the greatest educator in China, deeply engraved in the hearts of every educator. In our educational activities, we have always adhered to the idea of &#39;teaching according to students&#39; aptitude,&#39; designing adaptive synthetic biology popular science courses and activities for people of different ages and regions.</p>
<p>From children to teenagers, from university students to the general public, our educational activities have moved from inside the classroom to outside, gradually being accepted by hundreds and thousands of people. Our project and the principles of synthetic biology are gradually becoming integrated into people&#39;s lives.</p>
<p>We hope that through our efforts, more people can understand synthetic biology and see the vibrant development and bright future of life sciences. We hope that one day in the future, all our dreams will become a reality.</p>
